HEADWORD: Train oil
<hw>Train" oil`</hw> <pr>(oil`)</pr>. <ety>[D. or LG. <ets>traan</ets>
train oil, blubber (cf. Dan. & Sw. <ets>tran</ets>, G. <ets>thran</ets>)
+ E. <ets>oil</ets>.]</ety> <def>Oil procured from the blubber or fat of
whales, by boiling.</def>⟦br⟧
